nodes.text: The MPH power droid was a model of power droid. MPH-11 was an MPH power droid that worked in the spice mines of Kessel for the Pyke Syndicate. Along with the other droids enslaved in the mines, MPH-11 was freed during a droid revolt started by L3-37.
Years later, around 9 ABY, Peli Motto owned a MPH power droid to help her run Hangar 3-5 in Mos Eisley.
